  <Section Title="Declaration">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[class LogTargetStandardOut : public ILogTarget;]]></Code>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>LogTargetStandardOut</TypeRef> class is an <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.ILogTarget">ILogTarget</PageRef> implementation that writes messages to <TypeRef>std::cout</TypeRef>.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      Each line begins with a compact severity prefix, optionally followed by the scope and message text. The target can be configured to flush <TypeRef>std::cout</TypeRef> after every message.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
